premise_source_doc_sentence: Using third-generation recipes , Chronic Tacos ' made-to-order menu is customizable ; main items served include : tacos , burritos , and bowl-ritos .
Don Tacos is sold in 78-95 gram bags , in 47 gram cups that include dipping sauce , and in 50 gram boxes for supermarkets with dipping sauce .
Typical dishes include tacos or burritos prepared with Korean barbecue , such as kalbi or spicy chicken , and American foods such as french fries with kimchi .
Typical dishes include Korean tacos and bulgogi burritos .
Ingredients for the tacos and burritos include pork , chicken , beef , steak , or fish .
